item.title: Zeke Taylor | Biography
item.description: Zeke Taylor (born December 29, 2005) is an American actor, internet personality, YouTuber, computer programmer, and musician. He is best known for his role as the main character Jaden Newman in the American fantasy comedy web television series Merman Academy, as well as his roles in NicheZeke, Theories with Zeke, Hakeem Zeki in Lucid Nonsense and Danny Wests in The Witches.
